<tr>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; ">CMQ5</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">cm_2</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">Politicians usually do not tell us the true motives for their decisions.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; ">CMQ5</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">cm_3</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">Government agencies closely monitor all citizens.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; ">CMQ5</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">cm_4</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; ">Events which superficially seem to lack a connection are often the result of secret activities</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:left; border-bottom: double; ">CMQ5</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; border-bottom: double; ">cm_5</td>
<td style=" padding:0.2cm; text-align:left; vertical-align:top; text-align:center; border-bottom: double; ">There are secret organizations that greatly influence political decisions.</td>
